readme:
Service Usage

This service allows the consumer to retrieve the address details of a specific Agent Address that is linked to a specific Visa Application Identifier
The execution of this service is a step that is likely to occur when a Client has authorised correspondence be sent by care of their authorised agent that is within their visa application.

Service Behaviour

The consumer of this service will provide the following identifier which can be used to uniquely identify a visa application:
VisaApplicationId 1..1
ApplicantIdentifier 0..1

Service Variants

None

Service Dependencies

It is assumed that the service consumer has acquired a valid Visa Application Id, and optionally an Applicant Id from another source.
